config BR2_PACKAGE_OLLAMA
	bool "ollama"
	depends on BR2_aarch64
	help
	  Ollama — run Qwen and other LLMs locally via a REST API on port 11434.

	  This package installs the Ollama binary. Models are downloaded at
	  first boot and stored in /var/lib/ollama/models.

	  Default model: qwen2.5-coder:7b (configurable via /etc/ollama/config)

	  https://ollama.com
